This database contains a representative sample of titles (131) from the International Bureau of Education's International Textbook Collection. They cover a range of subjects and date from 1910 to 1975. As well as standard textbooks, teacher's manuals, atlases, dictionaries, guides, manuals and bibliographies are included. Subjects covered: Language education, mathematics, science, social sciences, religion and ethical education, aesthetic education, sports, skills and competencies.
